#. <section class="sutta" id="an3.8"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.8:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.8:0.2"
msgid "1. Bālavagga"
msgstr "1. Fools"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.8:0.3"
msgid "8. Sabyābajjhasutta"
msgstr "8. Hurtful"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an3.8:1.1"
msgid "“Tīhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bālo veditabbo."
msgstr "“A fool is known by three things."

msgctxt "an3.8:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi tīhi?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an3.8:1.3"
msgid ""
"Sabyābajjhena kāyakammena, sabyābajjhena vacīkammena, sabyābajjhena "
"manokammena … pe … abyābajjhena kāyakammena, abyābajjhena vacīkammena, "
"abyābajjhena manokammena."
msgstr ""
"Hurtful deeds by way of body, speech, and mind. … An astute person is known "
"by kind deeds by way of body, speech, and mind."

msgctxt "an3.8:1.4"
msgid "Imehi, kho, bhikkhave, tīhi dhammehi samannāgato paṇḍito veditabbo."
msgstr "These are the three things by which an astute person is known.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an3.8:2.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr "So you should train like this:"

msgctxt "an3.8:2.2"
msgid ""
"‘yehi tīhi dhammehi samannāgato bālo veditabbo te tayo dhamme "
"abhinivajjetvā, yehi tīhi dhammehi samannāgato paṇḍito veditabbo te tayo "
"dhamme samādāya vattissāmā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘We will reject the three qualities by which a fool is known, and we will "
"undertake and follow the three qualities by which an astute person is known.’"

msgctxt "an3.8:2.3"
msgid "Evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti."
msgstr "That’s how you should train.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.8:2.4"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
